# 📝 Guestbook App

A simple guestbook web app built with **Next.js** for the front-end and **Node.js (Express)** for the back-end.

---

## ✨ Features

- Submit messages to the guestbook.
- View a list of all messages.
- Simple and clean UI using Tailwind CSS.
- Backend API built with Express.
- Fully local and beginner-friendly.

